## 2. What each repo is for

| Repo | Role |
|------|------|
| **Service / app repo** | Application source; CI builds **Docker image**, pushes **tag** to ECR. |
| **`exotel_configs`** | **Helm chart** under `cqa/k8s/`, **values** under `cqa/k8s/values/` (`values.integration.yaml`, `values.qa.yaml`, `values.mum1.yaml`, `values.prod.yaml`). **Source of truth for intent.** |
| **`exotel_deployments`** | **Rendered** Kubernetes YAML (what ArgoCD applies). Usually **one folder per env**: `cqa/integration`, `cqa/qa`, `cqa/mum1`, `cqa/prod`. |
| **Argo CD** | Watches **`exotel_deployments`** (path per Application). **No Helm** in cluster — plain manifests. |

